вЂЋВ В В В В В В  <p>Oyasumi Punpun is a psychological manga about a variety of themes such as abuse, self-deprecation, childhood development, interpersonal relationships, and intimacy. While the story doesn't revolve around sex, it definitely plays a large role in establishing the themes and conflicts present in the story.
